{"tid":2381192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聘出獄手足任一日店員　營業額扣除成本全數出糧　元朗黃店：生意難做不忘開店初衷","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T13:04:12.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1511830b5ffd8ac3d9227fafcf525d7537edfc99","tid":2381192,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OW4N6qB8pXE8VQ75dpaOqap4caQ=/1024x576/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DJD7OWGN2RFI3K47M2CDOCPW3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOW4N6qB8pXE8VQ75dpaOqap4caQ%3D%2F1024x576%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDJD7OWGN2RFI3K47M2CDOCPW3E.jpg&h=5f39be83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年底逆巿開業的元朗黃店「亞萊泰菜」昨午（25日）在Facebook發文宣佈邀請一位本月出獄的反送中運動手足出任「一日店員」，並將今日營業額扣除成本後，全數出糧予該名手足，引來大批市民到場支持。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7dAeyL05yGwnnMT3bYcXatxFMd8=/5685x3787/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M2QLEZBI5FBEFFUXXI6MBCBNO4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7dAeyL05yGwnnMT3bYcXatxFMd8%3D%2F5685x3787%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM2QLEZBI5FBEFFUXXI6MBCBNO4.JPG&h=750db4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「亞萊泰菜」老闆Oscar昨日在Facebook發文撐手足後，即接到大量「懲罰」電話。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ti16ZowBPRfdFTCh6UleAN-qLC8=/5467x3641/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JAI6UD4BBFB5BA6YMC74DM5F7Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fti16ZowBPRfdFTCh6UleAN-qLC8%3D%2F5467x3641%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJAI6UD4BBFB5BA6YMC74DM5F7Q.JPG&h=4118e43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中午有近百人排隊「懲罰」，透過實際行動撐手足。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n念念不忘，必有迴響。去年底逆巿開業的元朗黃店「亞萊泰菜」昨午（25日）在Facebook發文宣佈邀請一位本月出獄的反送中運動手足出任「一日店員」，並將今日營業額扣除成本後，全數出糧予該名手足，結果今天開店前逾半小時已有十幾名巿民排隊，中午更有近百人排隊等候「懲罰」。<br />\n<br />\n社交網出帖後即收大批網民私訊稱要訂餐<br />\n年僅20歲「亞萊泰菜」老闆Oscar接受《蘋果》訪問時指，見到很多被捕及坐監的手足都有生活負擔，不少更是家庭主要經濟支柱，「佢哋被判刑坐監，我相信佢哋屋企人都會用晒啲積蓄」，故決定協助自己相識多時、出獄時銀行戶口只餘300多元的56歲手足李先生。<br />\n他坦言沒有想過網上發文公佈活動後，外界反應如此熱烈，指昨晚已不斷收到網民私訊稱要訂餐；餐廳為應付突如其來的「懲罰」，昨漏夜開始準備食材。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/VJKLVN7RMJESJD6JEUSXX6TXHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FVJKLVN7RMJESJD6JEUSXX6TXHA%2F&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=1bda8608\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210126%2FVJKLVN7RMJESJD6JEUSXX6TXHA%2F&h=892ad17c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210126/VJKLVN7RMJESJD6JEUSXX6TXHA/</a>"},{"pid":"5e4da09f627974c298976a34958c19dd61dd0454","tid":2381192,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3511139f3727154131067684d1315b6598e8f4a1","tid":2381192,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"一日？"},{"pid":"1bc131513bdd35f100614d2d149cf779accf6cd9","tid":2381192,"uid":107485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"型到"},{"pid":"e54d7112c26298af07f12f3f1b214e7b7cde3e19","tid":2381192,"uid":44831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3511139f3727154131067684d1315b6598e8f4a1","tid":2381192,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"一日？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"平過賣廣告"}]}